    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:8:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"2011 Redesign";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"href";s:51:"http://orderedlist.com/blog/articles/2011-redesign/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://orderedlist.com/blog/articles/2011-redesign/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"updated";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2011-01-03T23:07:06-05:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2011-01-03T22:47:00-05:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"summary";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:322:"<p>A new year, a new design. Interestingly enough, this redesign wasn&#8217;t because I got tired of the last one. It was because, with the addition of <a href="/blog/articles/welcome-jon-hoyt/">Hoyt</a> and <a href="/blog/articles/welcome-brandon-keepers/">Brandon</a>, I wanted to refocus the priorities of the site.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1428:"<p>A new year, a new design. Interestingly enough, this redesign wasn&#8217;t because I got tired of the last one. It was because, with the addition of <a href="/blog/articles/welcome-jon-hoyt/">Hoyt</a> and <a href="/blog/articles/welcome-brandon-keepers/">Brandon</a>, I wanted to refocus the priorities of the site.</p><p><img src="http://orderedlist.com/assets/4d229935dabe9d7c710000b8/article_full_width/ol10.jpg" title="Ordered List v10" alt="Ordered List v10" /></p>
<h2>Focus on Products</h2>
<p>Since the last redesign, we&#8217;ve launched <a href="http://get.harmonyapp.com">Harmony</a> and started <a href="http://speakerdeck.com">Speaker Deck</a>. We wanted to give those the attention they deserve. We&#8217;re proud of our work on these applications, and wanted to show them off more than just a small link or a blog post or two.</p>
<h2>Emphasize Development</h2>
<p>With our recent hires, I&#8217;m finally ready to admit that Ordered List, which started as a design and front-end studio in 2007, is now a full-service development and production shop. So I felt it was necessary to put more focus on our team&#8217;s <a href="/client-services/">extraordinary development skills</a>.</p>
<h2>A Fresh Start</h2>
<p>Lastly, I felt with all the change that was happening in the company, that I wanted to rethink and refine our message. I&#8217;m really happy with the results, and I hope you enjoy the redesign.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:16:"
        
